- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper focuses on the control and coordination of complex machines. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper mentions code generation for implementing the supervisor in software. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is another possible category as the paper discusses the implementation of the supervisory controller in software and embedded systems. 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses coordination of different components in a machine.
